REM ===========================================================================
REM A single file to include for any scripts outside of the "Common" script
REM directory. This way, all available tooling is available to a process with
REM a single call.If
REM 
REM Do not include this script within any script found inside of this folder
REM unless the include is within a function. This heavily increases the risk
REM of circular dependencies, which are difficult to troubleshoot in this
REM environment.
REM
REM The contents af this file are licensed to you by Ryan Singleton under the
REM MIT license.
REM ===========================================================================

REM This includes CoreFunctions, which includes the common strings.
REM Then it includes all of the remaining common functions.
Include MAPPATH_SCRIPTS "Common\FabFunctions.cod"
REM This will loads all common paths, shell functions, and context functions.
Include ScriptPath("ContextFunctions.cod")

REM Place your custom imports before, likely under a new Custom directory.

REM Include ScriptPath("Custom\CommonConnectors.cod")
REM Include ScriptPath("Custom\CommonSeams.cod")

REM If you customize this file, don't overwrite it when you want to update the 
REM scripts.